CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven women, including one wearing dot patterned dress with pleated skirt and dragonfly brooch, posed in Webster Hall with two toned walls for Thirtieth Anniversary of Girl Friends, Inc.
